Welcome to Level Up!

Here is how the half-day will go:

  • 1:00 - 1:10 pm: Join us for the all-team opening session. Here we will give you a warm welcome and provide detailed information on how to navigate Level Up.
  • 1:10 - 1:20 pm: Transition
  • 1:20 - 2:30 pm: Unconference sessions — are staff-led discussions in groups of 10 - 15; topics will cover working productively in government, managing people well, and boosting technical/agile skills
  • 2:30 - 2:40 pm: Transition
  • 2:40 - 3:40 pm: Snack party is a chance to “sit” and chat with team members from around TTS. Check out where you’re sitting, we assigned you a virtual table. Bring a snack!
  • 3:40 - 3:45 pm: Transition
  • 3:45 - 4:45 pm:Lessons learned sessions are staff-led discussions in groups of 10 - 15; these are stories of failure or wild success that others can learn from
  • 4:45 - 4:50 pm: Transition
  • 4:50 - 5:00 pm: All-team closing session. Now its time to say goodbye. Shout out what you learned (on slack) and hear about next steps.

Sign up for your sessions here. Space is limited, so sign up early.

Have any questions? Hit us up in #level-up.

Can’t make it? Let us know.
